 ٱلْمَوْتِ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ مُحِيطٌۢ بِٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"Or [the parable] of a violent cloudburst in the sky, with utter darkness, thunder and lightning: they put their fingers into their ears to keep out the peals of thunder, in terror of death; but God encompasses [with His might] all who deny the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/26.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":22027,"position":1,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22028,"position":2,"arabic":"كَصَيِّبٍۢ","translation":"মতো বৃষ্টিপাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22029,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22030,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","translation":"আকাশ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22031,"position":5,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"তার মধ্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22032,"position":6,"arabic":"ظُلُمَـٰتٌۭ","translation":"অন্ধকার","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22033,"position":7,"arabic":"وَرَعْدٌۭ","translation":"এবং গর্জন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22034,"position":8,"arabic":"وَبَرْقٌۭ","translation":"ও বিদ্যুৎচমক","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22035,"position":9,"arabic":"يَجْعَلُونَ","translation":"তারা রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22036,"position":10,"arabic":"أَصَـٰبِعَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের আঙ্গুলগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22037,"position":11,"arabic":"فِىٓ","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22038,"position":12,"arabic":"ءَاذَانِهِم","translation":"তাদের কানগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_019_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22039,"position":13,"arabic":"مِّنَ","tran